Challenges for kids after they study all demo codes:

1. Type on keyboard via TV remote control buttons
uses: demo 11 and demo 4


2. Every time you clap with hands the RGB LED change it's color randomly
uses: demo 5 and demo 7

3. Controlling servo motor with capacitive sensor, each time you grab D14 and GND the servo motor change it's angle depend on how strong you press.
uses: demo 10 and 19

4. Display on LED matrix light bars which stack up when you get closer
uses: demo 6 and 20

